{"tid":2375733,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"毆傷美國駐港領館保安 裝修工判入小欖精神病院","createTime":"2021-01-22T08:55:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-22T13:32:59.000Z","uid":240362,"like":7,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"f97d641dd47378b705240153ed5e726367b57df6","tid":2375733,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T08:55:05.000Z","msg":"2021-01-22 16:34 <br />\n<br />\n裝修工人去年在美國領事館外，將一名保安員毆至頭破血流，須送院縫針；又揮棍打破英國領事館的保安室玻璃窗。他早前承認傷人及刑事毁壞罪，今在東區裁判法院被判入住小欖精神病院。<br />\n<br />\n被告張文達（35歲）承認在去年8月25日，在中環美國領事館外，非法及惡意傷害Raphael Todd；以及在年2月15日，非法損毁英國駐港總領事館的保安室玻璃窗。"},{"pid":"87cce8565b8a764cf17e5d22b57c0b2b6441dab3","tid":2375733,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T08:55:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ebf3a2b0a0c0d720c11b4a8a718931b93bf93ec","tid":2375733,"uid":76804,"like":2,"dislike":15,"score":-13,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T08:56:16.000Z","msg":"痴撚線正常人無啦啦要入精神病院<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0197e83d01486594389a91a13ea770a11fb6da16","tid":2375733,"uid":251732,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T08:56:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d90bfd7f7c2dc3ce4939cb70ac9f7b7db638535","tid":2375733,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T08:57:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /